phics hog.So why did i metion that I stopped playing the remastered games?I had a feeling that the last scene in the last mission would get me wanting to play the other games again.And I wasnt dissapointed when I heard something familiar in the last cutscene. Im looking forward to playing homeworld 1 again after this. And I hope we see more new homeworld coming soon!"
