 have ever done so. Sad.Edit: Oh and you can't re-bind keys. For a left-handed person this is almost deal breaker. Bought a keyboard which allows that but it's hardly ideal and sometimes doesn't work correctly. DEVS QUIT DOING THIS!!!"
